<li id="cite_note-55"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-55">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">"All Saints' Day", <i>The Oxford Dictionary of the Christian Church</i>, 3rd edition, ed. E. A. Livingstone. <a href="/wiki/Oxford_University_Press" title="Oxford University Press">Oxford University Press</a>, 1997. pp.41–42</span>
