<li id="cite_note-96"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-96">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="/wiki/Margaret_Aston" title="Margaret Aston">Aston, Margaret</a>. <i>Broken Idols of the English Reformation</i>. Cambridge University Press, 2015. pp.475–477</span>
