oween" title="Template talk:Halloween"><abbr title="Discuss this template" style="background:black; color:orange;;background:none transparent;border:none;box-shadow:none;padding:0;">t</abbr></a></li><li class="nv-edit"><a href="/wiki/Special:EditPage/Template:Halloween" title="Special:EditPage/Template:Halloween"><abbr title="Edit this template" style="background:black; color:orange;;background:none transparent;border:none;box-shadow:none;padding:0;">e</abbr></a></li></ul></div><div id="Halloween" style="font-size:114%;margin:0 4em"><a class="mw-selflink selflink"><span style="color:orange">Halloween</span></a></div></th></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="navbox-group" style="background:black; color:orange;width:1%"><span style="color:orange;">Main topics</span></th><td class="navbox-list-with-group navbox-list navbox-odd" style="width:100%;padding:0"><div style="padding:0 0.25em">
